      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PET DETECTIVE (1) goes very well this trip starting 23 times for 11 wins and 11 minors. Hit the frame latest (16.78) when second at Murray Bridge in a Grade 4/5. Rates a leading player. JABUK (2) boasts a strong record this journey here with seven wins and four minors from 12 tries. In the money last time at Murray Bridge (16.95) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 2.25 lengths third. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. CASH PAID (7) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 17.04 beating Techno Kelli. Has good speed and will be prominent from out wide. Should feature again. ZIPPING ROVE (8) racing over this distance brings the best out in him.",
